</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="82.[151,1437,290,929]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">Habitat. Infralittoral species, in lagoons, from brackish to slightly hypersaline, in shallows on sand near seagrass (Miller 1986).</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="82.[151,1437,290,929]" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">
Geographic distribution. Mediterranean. Recorded from the central and southern Mediterranean from Sicily, 
<collectingCountry box="[151,216,902,928]" name="Libya" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">Libya</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[270,353,902,928]" name="Tunisia" pageId="82" pageNumber="83">Tunisia</collectingCountry>
(Miller 1986; 
